text: Kalnovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Vyazovsky Selsoviet, Chernoyarsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 102 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located on the Podgornoye Lake. == References == Category:Rural localities in Chernoyarsky District
title: Kalnovka
